/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;स्नातक: सुचना प्रौद्योगिकी</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म : 05/01/1981</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म स्थान : जसरा,&nbsp; उत्तर प्रदेश&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य : निजी कम्पनी मे कार्यत&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य स्थल : कोलकाता, पश्चिम बंगाल&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>रूचि : साहित्य पठन/लेखन</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 38040, NULL, NULL, 'Sushil24.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/Sushil24.jpg', NULL),
(180, 'Dr. Arjun   Pangannavar', 'Yallappa', '1951-06-29', '8971171477 ', '9448762733', 'arjun_pangannavar@yahoo.in', 'Smt Gowramma(wife)', 'RS# 173/B/5, H.No-71 Vidya Nagar, Opp Sai Mandir', 'GOKAK-591307', 'Gokak', 'Karnataka', 591307, 'India', 'Shweta Pangannavar', 2147483647, 'State Bank of India', 'ADB Branch GOKAK Code-1814', 'SBIN0001814', 'ADNPP6523B', 'Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite', 'Dr. Arjun Y. Pangannavar', 'Hindi', 'Poetry', 1, '1', '1', '<p>Poet Arjun Y. Pangannavar&rsquo;s&nbsp;&nbsp; the book <strong>&ldquo;Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite&rdquo; comprises 53 </strong>poems in Kannada, focuses on his own experience in love and life. The book has fifty-five poems on nature, fate, life&rsquo;s different looks and stages and love&rsquo;s different faces, gifts, conversations, pleasures, longings, despairs, soothing and commemoration. These poems were composed during specific period on account of the happenings and instant feelings from stubborn and maddened heart, poems flew not from mind to write but from the bottom of heart and its instant reaction; so these poems are the memories of those events that I depicted them in form of poems, some are composed to eternalized the love and loved one, it is not the physical attraction&rsquo;s love and its feelings but soul&rsquo;s longing to one with the soul that attracted each other, love is not love that alters when finds alteration, it is the real love that has no bindings of time and purpose; the heart perception is strange, it shares its feelings, not passion, with the those whoever feels so by meets; love must be enduring but should not be erotic, meanwhile love is for all so it must also be eternalized. So are my poems, may diffuse love-honey perfume to the readers, but they are prayed not to despise them, they are my love.</p>\r\n', '<p>&ldquo;ಎಲ್ಲ 53 ಕವನಗಳನ್ನು ಅಕ್ಟೋಬರ 1977 ರಿಂದ ನವ್ಹೆಂಬರ 2021ರ ಅವಧಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ರಚಿಸಿರುತ್ತೇನೆ. ಬಾಲ್ಯದಲಿ ತಿಳುವಳಕೆ ಬಂದಾಗಿನಿಂದ ಇಲ್ಲಿವರೆಗೆ ಬದುಕಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಹಲವಾರು ಘಟನೆಗಳು ಘಟಿಸಿದವು; ಈ ಘಟನೆಗಳನ್ನು ನನ್ನನ್ನು ನಾಲ್ಕು ಸೆಳೆತಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಎಳೆದವು: ಮೊದಲನೆಯದಾಗಿ, 1957ರಿಂದ 1980ರ ವರೆಗಿನ ಬದುಕಿನ ಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿಯ ಅನುಭವಗಳು ನನ್ನನ್ನು ಕಿಶೋರಾವಸ್ಥೆಯ, ಯವ್ವನದ ಸ್ನೇಹ ಮೋಜು ಮಸ್ತಿ ಮುಗ್ದ ಪ್ರೇಮದ ಕನಸುಗಳ ಪರ್ವ.&rdquo; ಕವಿ ಅರ್ಜುನ ಪಂಗಣ್ಣವರರ ಈ ಮನದ ನುಡಿಯ ಅವರ ಕವನ ಕೃತಿ ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ:ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼಯು ಮನುಷ್ಯನ ಬದುಕಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಬರುವ ಎಲ್ಲ ನಿರಂತರ ಪ್ರೇಮಗಳ ಕನ್ನಡಿಯಾಗಿದೆ; ಬಾಲ್ಯಾವಸ್ಥೆಯಿಂದ ಮುಪ್ಪಿನಾವಸ್ಥೆವರೆಗೂ ಸಂದರ್ಭ, ಸಮಯಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಘಟಿಸುವ ಅನಿರೀಕ್ಷಿತ ಘಟನೆಗಳು, ಅವುಗಳ ಹಿಂದಿನ ಭಾವನೆಗಳು ಮತ್ತು ಮನಸ್ಸಿನ ತುಡಿತಗಳು ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ: ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼಯಲ್ಲಿ ಸೂಸಿ ಬಂದಿವೆ, ಶೀರ್ಷಕೆ ಅರ್ಥಪೂರ್ಣವಾಗಿದೆ; ಯವೌನದ ಪ್ರೇಮವು ದೇಹದ ಆಕರ್ಷಣಿಯದಾಗಿರದೇ ಎಲ್ಲ ಸಂದರ್ಭದಲ್ಲೂ, ಕಾಲದಲ್ಲೂ ನಿರಂತರ ಅತ್ಮಗಳ ಮಿಲನದ ಹಂಬಲ ಹೊಂದಿಬೇಕು. ಕವಿ ಅರ್ಜುನ ಪಂಗಣ್ಣವರರು ಈಗಾಗಲೆ ಕನ್ನಡ ಮತ್ತು ಇಂಗ್ಲೀಷಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಸಾಕಷ್ಟು ಸಾಹಿತ್ಯವನ್ನು ಕಲೆ ಮತ್ತು ಸಮಾಜ ವಿಜ್ಞಾನ ಕೇತ್ರದಲ್ಲಿ ಕೊಡುಗೆ ನೀಡಿರುವರು,ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ:ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼ ಕವನ ಕೃತಿಯೂ ಓದುಗರ ಮನಮೆಚ್ಚವ ಕೃತಿಯಾಗಲೆಂದು ಶುಭಕೋರುವೆ ಮತ್ತು ಅಭಿನಂದಿಸುವೆ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;ಡಾ. ಕವಿತಾ ಕುಸುಗಲ್ಲ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ಇಂಗ್ಲೀಷ ವಿಭಾಗ, ರಾಣಿ ಚನ್ನಮ್ಮ ವಿಶ್ವವಿದ್ಯಾಲಯ ಬೆಳಗಾವಿ</p>\r\n', '<p>Prof, Dr. Arjun Y Pangannavar is a versatile writer and poet in Kannada and English language. He was born on 29th June 1951 at Gokak-Falls in labor-class tribal family. Shri Yallappa Pangannavar and Smt Holhevva were his parents; He studied Economics, English and Kannada Literature at graduation level and MA &amp; PhD in economics.&nbsp; He started his lecturer career from 1977 and retired (2011) as Associated Professor of Economics and Principal (2014) from a reputed graduate-colleges. He is guide to PhD research scholars from Bharathiar University Coimbatore (TN) India&mdash;one is awarded PhD. Kannada University Hampi, Karnataka has nominated him as a member of Advisory Committee of `The Chair of Valmiki Studies&rsquo;.&nbsp; Micro-finance, women empowerment, rural development, and economic issues are the special area of his research. He has presented research papers in national and international seminars, conferences and published in national and international journals, 11 research works in ResearchGate wherein 60+ thousand scholars, researchers and professors read and share his work world-wide; his works have been cited in a good number of theses and research papers, world-wide. He writes articles regularly for Kannada-monthly &lsquo;Valmiki Karnataka&rsquo;. He authored 26 books, including economics, prose, and poetry. &ldquo;Shrimad Valmiki Ramayana Maha-Kaavya Darshanm (Part-1, 2 &amp; 3)&rdquo; is his great contribution<strong>. </strong>Now his book on <strong>&ldquo;Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite&rdquo;,</strong> poems in Kannada, focuses on his own experience in love and life</p>\r\n', 8189, NULL, NULL, 'arjun.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/arjun.jpg', NULL),
(181, 'Dr. Arjun   Pangannavar', 'Yallappa', '1951-06-29', '8971171477 ', '9448762733', 'arjun_pangannavar@yahoo.in', 'Smt Gowramma(wife)', 'RS# 173/B/5, H.No-71 Vidya Nagar, Opp Sai Mandir', 'GOKAK-591307', 'Gokak', 'Karnataka', 591307, 'India', 'Shweta Pangannavar', 2147483647, 'State Bank of India', 'ADB Branch GOKAK Code-1814', 'SBIN0001814', 'ADNPP6523B', 'Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite', 'Dr. Arjun Y. Pangannavar', 'Hindi', 'Poetry', 1, '1', '1', '<p>Poet Arjun Y. Pangannavar&rsquo;s&nbsp;&nbsp; the book <strong>&ldquo;Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite&rdquo; comprises 53 </strong>poems in Kannada, focuses on his own experience in love and life. The book has fifty-five poems on nature, fate, life&rsquo;s different looks and stages and love&rsquo;s different faces, gifts, conversations, pleasures, longings, despairs, soothing and commemoration. These poems were composed during specific period on account of the happenings and instant feelings from stubborn and maddened heart, poems flew not from mind to write but from the bottom of heart and its instant reaction; so these poems are the memories of those events that I depicted them in form of poems, some are composed to eternalized the love and loved one, it is not the physical attraction&rsquo;s love and its feelings but soul&rsquo;s longing to one with the soul that attracted each other, love is not love that alters when finds alteration, it is the real love that has no bindings of time and purpose; the heart perception is strange, it shares its feelings, not passion, with the those whoever feels so by meets; love must be enduring but should not be erotic, meanwhile love is for all so it must also be eternalized. So are my poems, may diffuse love-honey perfume to the readers, but they are prayed not to despise them, they are my love.</p>\r\n', '<p>&ldquo;ಎಲ್ಲ 53 ಕವನಗಳನ್ನು ಅಕ್ಟೋಬರ 1977 ರಿಂದ ನವ್ಹೆಂಬರ 2021ರ ಅವಧಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ರಚಿಸಿರುತ್ತೇನೆ. ಬಾಲ್ಯದಲಿ ತಿಳುವಳಕೆ ಬಂದಾಗಿನಿಂದ ಇಲ್ಲಿವರೆಗೆ ಬದುಕಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಹಲವಾರು ಘಟನೆಗಳು ಘಟಿಸಿದವು; ಈ ಘಟನೆಗಳನ್ನು ನನ್ನನ್ನು ನಾಲ್ಕು ಸೆಳೆತಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಎಳೆದವು: ಮೊದಲನೆಯದಾಗಿ, 1957ರಿಂದ 1980ರ ವರೆಗಿನ ಬದುಕಿನ ಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿಯ ಅನುಭವಗಳು ನನ್ನನ್ನು ಕಿಶೋರಾವಸ್ಥೆಯ, ಯವ್ವನದ ಸ್ನೇಹ ಮೋಜು ಮಸ್ತಿ ಮುಗ್ದ ಪ್ರೇಮದ ಕನಸುಗಳ ಪರ್ವ.&rdquo; ಕವಿ ಅರ್ಜುನ ಪಂಗಣ್ಣವರರ ಈ ಮನದ ನುಡಿಯ ಅವರ ಕವನ ಕೃತಿ ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ:ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼಯು ಮನುಷ್ಯನ ಬದುಕಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಬರುವ ಎಲ್ಲ ನಿರಂತರ ಪ್ರೇಮಗಳ ಕನ್ನಡಿಯಾಗಿದೆ; ಬಾಲ್ಯಾವಸ್ಥೆಯಿಂದ ಮುಪ್ಪಿನಾವಸ್ಥೆವರೆಗೂ ಸಂದರ್ಭ, ಸಮಯಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಘಟಿಸುವ ಅನಿರೀಕ್ಷಿತ ಘಟನೆಗಳು, ಅವುಗಳ ಹಿಂದಿನ ಭಾವನೆಗಳು ಮತ್ತು ಮನಸ್ಸಿನ ತುಡಿತಗಳು ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ: ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼಯಲ್ಲಿ ಸೂಸಿ ಬಂದಿವೆ, ಶೀರ್ಷಕೆ ಅರ್ಥಪೂರ್ಣವಾಗಿದೆ; ಯವೌನದ ಪ್ರೇಮವು ದೇಹದ ಆಕರ್ಷಣಿಯದಾಗಿರದೇ ಎಲ್ಲ ಸಂದರ್ಭದಲ್ಲೂ, ಕಾಲದಲ್ಲೂ ನಿರಂತರ ಅತ್ಮಗಳ ಮಿಲನದ ಹಂಬಲ ಹೊಂದಿಬೇಕು. ಕವಿ ಅರ್ಜುನ ಪಂಗಣ್ಣವರರು ಈಗಾಗಲೆ ಕನ್ನಡ ಮತ್ತು ಇಂಗ್ಲೀಷಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಸಾಕಷ್ಟು ಸಾಹಿತ್ಯವನ್ನು ಕಲೆ ಮತ್ತು ಸಮಾಜ ವಿಜ್ಞಾನ ಕೇತ್ರದಲ್ಲಿ ಕೊಡುಗೆ ನೀಡಿರುವರು,ʻಚೈತ್ರಗಾಳಿ:ಪ್ರೇಮಗೀತೆʼ ಕವನ ಕೃತಿಯೂ ಓದುಗರ ಮನಮೆಚ್ಚವ ಕೃತಿಯಾಗಲೆಂದು ಶುಭಕೋರುವೆ ಮತ್ತು ಅಭಿನಂದಿಸುವೆ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;ಡಾ. ಕವಿತಾ ಕುಸುಗಲ್ಲ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ಇಂಗ್ಲೀಷ ವಿಭಾಗ, ರಾಣಿ ಚನ್ನಮ್ಮ ವಿಶ್ವವಿದ್ಯಾಲಯ ಬೆಳಗಾವಿ</p>\r\n', '<p>Prof, Dr. Arjun Y Pangannavar is a versatile writer and poet in Kannada and English language. He was born on 29th June 1951 at Gokak-Falls in labor-class tribal family. Shri Yallappa Pangannavar and Smt Holhevva were his parents; He studied Economics, English and Kannada Literature at graduation level and MA &amp; PhD in economics.&nbsp; He started his lecturer career from 1977 and retired (2011) as Associated Professor of Economics and Principal (2014) from a reputed graduate-colleges. He is guide to PhD research scholars from Bharathiar University Coimbatore (TN) India&mdash;one is awarded PhD. Kannada University Hampi, Karnataka has nominated him as a member of Advisory Committee of `The Chair of Valmiki Studies&rsquo;.&nbsp; Micro-finance, women empowerment, rural development, and economic issues are the special area of his research. He has presented research papers in national and international seminars, conferences and published in national and international journals, 11 research works in ResearchGate wherein 60+ thousand scholars, researchers and professors read and share his work world-wide; his works have been cited in a good number of theses and research papers, world-wide. He writes articles regularly for Kannada-monthly &lsquo;Valmiki Karnataka&rsquo;. He authored 26 books, including economics, prose, and poetry. &ldquo;Shrimad Valmiki Ramayana Maha-Kaavya Darshanm (Part-1, 2 &amp; 3)&rdquo; is his great contribution<strong>. </strong>Now his book on <strong>&ldquo;Chaitra Gali: Prema Gite&rdquo;,</strong> poems in Kannada, focuses on his own experience in love and life</p>\r\n', 8189, NULL, NULL, 'arjun1.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/arjun1.jpg', NULL),
(182, 'सुशील पाण्डेय ', 'शिव बचन पाण्डेय ', '1981-01-05', '8240913844', '8448579933', 'sushilara_mim@rediffmail.com', 'Rashmi Pandey ', 'Vill- Motirampur, Post- Kalyanpur, Dist- Bhojpur', 'Shiv mandir', 'Bihiya', 'Bihar', 802154, 'India', 'Sushil Kumar Pandey', 2147483647, 'ICICI BANK', 'Mango', 'ICIC0001412', 'BOHPP1997P', 'चिट्ठीयाँ', 'सुशील पाण्डेय ', 'Hindi', 'Poetry', 1, '1', '2', '<p>यह किताब पूर्व प्रेमिका को लिखे गये प्रेमपत्र का काव्य रूपांतरण है जिसका उद्देश्य अनकही भावनाओं को इस किताब के माध्यम से उसके आज मे खलल डाले बिना उस तक पहुंचाना है। जीवन के आपाधापी मे बहुत सी बातें जो बता देनी चाहिए समय रहते पर मध्यमवर्गीय युवाओं की ये असमंजस हमेशा से रही है और लाजिम भी है बेरोजगारी के दौर मे परिवार के अपेक्षाओं पर खरा उतरने के जद्दोजहद मे आंतरिक बहुत सी भावनायें अंदर ही अंदर दफन हो जाती हैं। जिनका उस तक पहुंचना आवश्यक है जिसके लिए वो आईं हैं भले देर से ही सही पर इस बात का ख्याल हमेशा हो कि किसी का वर्तमान प्रभावित ना हो।</p>\r\n', '<p>मै कुछ बताना चाहता हूं तुम्हे&hellip;... और साथ ही धन्यवाद भी करना चाहता हूं उस सबके लिए जो तुमने मुझे दिया इन साथ साथ बिताये वर्षों मे।<br />\r\nजो मेरे लिए अब भी बहुत उपयोगी साबित हो रहा है एक सफल वैवाहिक जीवन व्यतीत करने में उस सबके लिए तुम्हारा आभार<br />\r\nकैसे तुमसे जुड़ाव ने मेरी जिंदगी को सकारात्मक मोड़ दे दिया?<br />\r\nकैसे हर चौराहे पर प्यार करने वाले को तुमसे हो जाने के बाद फिर किसी से हुआ ही नही?<br />\r\nकैसे किसी के समक्ष कमजोर तक न दिखने वाला तुम्हारे सामने फूट-फूटकर रोना सीख गया?<br />\r\nकैसे कभी किसी की चिंता न करनेवाले ने तुम्हारी परवाह को ही अपने जीवन का अहम हिस्सा बना लिया?<br />\r\nकैसे इन थोड़े से वर्षों ने मुझे तेरा हमेशा ख्याल रखने की खातिर खुद की सबसे ज्यादा चिंता करना सिखा दिया?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>हां ये भी है कई बार बहुत तकलीफ भी दिया होगा मैने, पर सच मानो ऐसा जान-बूझकर कर कभी नही हुआ हां ठीक है उसके लिए माफी जरूर नही मांगा मैने, पर भावनाओं मे कलुषिता का न होना ही बिन मांगे क्षमा का हकदार तो बना ही देता है मुझे।</p>\r\n', '<p>नाम&nbsp; : सुशील कुमार पाण्डेय&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>शिक्षा : स्नातकोत्तर (प्रबंधन),</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;स्नातक: सुचना प्रौद्योगिकी</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म : 05/01/1981</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म स्थान : जसरा,&nbsp; उत्तर प्रदेश&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य : निजी कम्पनी मे कार्यत&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य स्थल : कोलकाता, पश्चिम बंगाल&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>रूचि : साहित्य पठन/लेखन</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 38040, NULL, NULL, 'Sushil25.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/Sushil25.jpg', NULL),
(183, 'सुशील पाण्डेय ', 'शिव बचन पाण्डेय ', '1981-01-05', '8240913844', '8448579933', 'sushilara_mim@rediffmail.com', 'Rashmi Pandey ', 'Vill- Motirampur, Post- Kalyanpur, Dist- Bhojpur', 'Shiv mandir', 'Bihiya', 'Bihar', 802154, 'India', 'Sushil Kumar Pandey', 2147483647, 'ICICI BANK', 'Mango', 'ICIC0001412', 'BOHPP1997P', 'चिट्ठीयाँ', 'सुशील पाण्डेय ', 'Hindi', 'Poetry', 1, '1', '2', '<p>यह किताब पूर्व प्रेमिका को लिखे गये प्रेमपत्र का काव्य रूपांतरण है जिसका उद्देश्य अनकही भावनाओं को इस किताब के माध्यम से उसके आज मे खलल डाले बिना उस तक पहुंचाना है। जीवन के आपाधापी मे बहुत सी बातें जो बता देनी चाहिए समय रहते पर मध्यमवर्गीय युवाओं की ये असमंजस हमेशा से रही है और लाजिम भी है बेरोजगारी के दौर मे परिवार के अपेक्षाओं पर खरा उतरने के जद्दोजहद मे आंतरिक बहुत सी भावनायें अंदर ही अंदर दफन हो जाती हैं। जिनका उस तक पहुंचना आवश्यक है जिसके लिए वो आईं हैं भले देर से ही सही पर इस बात का ख्याल हमेशा हो कि किसी का वर्तमान प्रभावित ना हो।</p>\r\n', '<p>मै कुछ बताना चाहता हूं तुम्हे&hellip;... और साथ ही धन्यवाद भी करना चाहता हूं उस सबके लिए जो तुमने मुझे दिया इन साथ साथ बिताये वर्षों मे।<br />\r\nजो मेरे लिए अब भी बहुत उपयोगी साबित हो रहा है एक सफल वैवाहिक जीवन व्यतीत करने में उस सबके लिए तुम्हारा आभार<br />\r\nकैसे तुमसे जुड़ाव ने मेरी जिंदगी को सकारात्मक मोड़ दे दिया?<br />\r\nकैसे हर चौराहे पर प्यार करने वाले को तुमसे हो जाने के बाद फिर किसी से हुआ ही नही?<br />\r\nकैसे किसी के समक्ष कमजोर तक न दिखने वाला तुम्हारे सामने फूट-फूटकर रोना सीख गया?<br />\r\nकैसे कभी किसी की चिंता न करनेवाले ने तुम्हारी परवाह को ही अपने जीवन का अहम हिस्सा बना लिया?<br />\r\nकैसे इन थोड़े से वर्षों ने मुझे तेरा हमेशा ख्याल रखने की खातिर खुद की सबसे ज्यादा चिंता करना सिखा दिया?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>हां ये भी है कई बार बहुत तकलीफ भी दिया होगा मैने, पर सच मानो ऐसा जान-बूझकर कर कभी नही हुआ हां ठीक है उसके लिए माफी जरूर नही मांगा मैने, पर भावनाओं मे कलुषिता का न होना ही बिन मांगे क्षमा का हकदार तो बना ही देता है मुझे।</p>\r\n', '<p>नाम&nbsp; : सुशील कुमार पाण्डेय&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>शिक्षा : स्नातकोत्तर (प्रबंधन),</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;स्नातक: सुचना प्रौद्योगिकी</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म : 05/01/1981</p>\r\n\r\n<p>जन्म स्थान : जसरा,&nbsp; उत्तर प्रदेश&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य : निजी कम्पनी मे कार्यत&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>कार्य स्थल : कोलकाता, पश्चिम बंगाल&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>रूचि : साहित्य पठन/लेखन</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 38040, NULL, NULL, 'Sushil26.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/Sushil26.jpg', NULL),
(184, 'Dr. Md. Zubair Ahmad', 'Md. Tabarak', '1971-01-17', '9030878911', '9948336140', 'zubair.zoya@gmail.com', 'Nikhat Jahan', 'B-9, Type-II, Staff Quarter, MANUU Campus', 'Gachibowli', 'Hyderabad', 'Telangana', 500032, 'India', 'Md. Zubair Ahmad', 2147483647, 'Indian Overseas Bank', 'Gachibowli', 'IOBA0001879', 'AKDPA4696D', 'Implementation of automation in academic libraries', 'Dr. Md. Zubair Ahmad and Dr. Gorantla Siva Prasad', 'English', 'Academics', 36, '1', '1', '<p><strong>IMPLEMENTATION OF AUTOMATION IN ACADEMIC LIBRARIES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dr. Md. Zubair Ahmad</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(MA, MLIS, M. Phil, Ph. D, SET AP&amp;TS, NET-UGC in Library &amp; Information Science and PGDCA)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dr.</strong> <strong>Gorantla Siva Prasad</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(M. Sc, MLIS, M. Phil, Ph. D (Geology), Ph. D (Library &amp; Information Science) and PGDCS)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the book:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Library whether academic, special or a public library, being the backbone of any organization, the basic function of the library is to identify, select, collect, process, store and disseminate the information at the right time to the right person as and when required. It is an open fact that libraries are an important institution for any country. So that special type of manpower is required to manage this type of institution. This type of manpower can be prepared by importing specialized professional education in the field of library and information science. Library and information science has been an important branch of education in this modern age. So, library automation has played a vital role in library services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Library and information science professionals are confronted today by the rapidly changing environment. Library automation and implementation of computers for routine activities as well as non-routine activities of the library has become almost a necessity and is being hotly discussed and debated in all professional gatherings. Therefore, the library and information professionals need to develop their level of competency and understanding the changes in the technology so that they can articulate for adopting the same for bringing improvement in the services of any library.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The automation of libraries can be regarded as the way to escape from the pressing problems of everyday life in a library like ordering, processing&nbsp;and&nbsp;cataloguing&nbsp;of books, answering reference questions, tracing lost books, etc. Library automation certainly can simplify and solve most of these tasks, but it must be built upon a strong foundation. The function of an automated library in the present era is not only limited to a computer system which manages one or several of the library&rsquo;s in-house functions but it also deals with the emerging technologies, standards and formats, software, hardware, resource sharing, library networking, web OPAC (Online Public Access Catalogue) and other aspects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The whole extent of the present book, for the sake of convenience and transparency, has been discussed under the following six broad chapters:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chapter 1:</strong> Chapter one deals with the introductory part of this study, which includes Introduction, Automation, Library automation, Statement of the problems, Significance of the study, Aims and objectives, Hypothesis formulation, Scope and limitations, Methodology, Population and Sampling, and Scheme of work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chapter 2:</strong> Chapter two deals with the review of related literature on library automation. Literature collected from books, conference proceedings, journals, survey reports&nbsp;and&nbsp;the internet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chapter 3: Chapter three deals with the methodology adopted for the study, which describes the research problems, design, sources of data, tools, population and sampling, data analysis and statistical techniques used.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chapter 4: Chapter four deals with depict the library automation and its facets, history of library automation, definition, aims and objectives, essential for the library automation. It also provides an insight into the various aspects of library automation including the concept, scope and trend of library automation, along with the areas and activities of library automation and the various hardware and software considerations. It also deals with problems of automation, such as social, economic, environmental, technical, and such other problems. It also deals with the library automation software available in the market, both commercial and open access library automation software.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chapter 5: Chapter five deals exclusively with the analysis and interpretation of data. The data collected through questionnaires and interview schedules designed for the study will be analyzed and interpreted by the way of tables and graphs. Analyze these data in the light of hypothesis and research questionnaires and prevailing theories, drawing conclusions that are as amenable to theory formation as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chapter 6: Chapter six deals with the findings, conclusion and suggestions of the present study. Findings in the light of data analysis and interpretation as found in the previous chapter with the help of questionnaires received from librarians and users of these libraries. This chapter also deals with conclusions and suggestions rendered for solutions. On the basis of analysis and interpretation of data, the researcher would like to arrive at specific findings and important suggestions will be configured based on the findings of the study and test the hypotheses and fulfill the objectives of the study.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This book is based on Ph. D. thesis submitted to the Bharathiar University, Coimbatore. This book is helpful for students doing library and information science courses (Certificate, Diploma, BLIS and MLIS); research scholars (M.Phil and Ph.D); library professionals, knowledge managers, academic institutions and other communities planning to implement modern tools and technology in their libraries. This book also provides a practical approach to various new technologies implemented in various libraries. In this direction this book provides ideas to its readers about the approaches pertaining to practical implementations of modern tools and technologies, software platforms to automate their libraries, and other related technical aspects required for libraries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Target audience: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The target audience of this book will be students doing library science courses; research scholars working in the field of library and information science and library professionals. It will also guide to professionals working that includes Librarians, Officers in libraries, Information Scientists, consultants, Trainers, Students, Researchers and other library communities who are planning to adopt and implement modern tools and technologies in their libraries.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>IMPLEMENTATION OF AUTOMATION IN ACADEMIC LIBRARIES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>About the Book</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Library whether academic, special or a public library, being the backbone of any organization, the basic function of the library is to identify, select, collect, process, store and disseminate the information at right time to the right person as and when required. This book is helpful for students doing library and information science courses, research scholars, library professionals, knowledge managers, and other communities planning to implement modern tools and technology in their libraries. This book also provides a practical approach to various new technologies implemented in various libraries. In this direction this book provides ideas to its readers about the approaches pertaining to practical implementations of modern tools and technologies, software platforms to automate their libraries, and other related technical aspects required for libraries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The target audience of this book will be students doing library science courses; research scholars working in the field of library and information science and library professionals. It will also guide to professionals working that includes Librarians, Officers in libraries, Information Scientists, consultants, Trainers, Students, Researchers and other library communities who are planning to adopt and implement modern tools and technologies in their libraries.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>About the Authors</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dr. Md. Zubair Ahmad</strong> is working with MANUU, Hyderabad. He has more than 22 years of experience in his professional area. He has passed MA (Urdu), BLIS from Jamia Millia Islamia, New Delhi, MLIS from Delhi University, M. Phil from Alagappa University, Karaikudi, Ph. D in Library and Information Science from Bharathiar University, Coimbatore, PGDCA from Annamalai University and also qualified UGC NET December 2013 &amp; June 2014, SET TS&amp;AP February 2015. He was awarded the Mirza Mahmood Baig Memorial Scholarship in his BLIS programme. He has published several research papers and articles in reputed journals and conference proceedings besides contributing chapters in books. He has participated and presented research papers in several National and International Seminars and Conferences. He is the life member of Indian Library Association and Telangana Library Association.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dr. Gorantla Siva Prasad</strong> is presently working as Senior Grade Lecturer in Library Science (College Librarian), Government College for Women (Autonomous) Guntur has more than 26 years of experience. He has passed M. Sc (Marine Geology &amp; Computer Science), MLIS from Annamalai University, M. Phil (Computer Science) from Sri Krishnadevaraya University, Ph. D (Geology) from Andhra University, Ph. D (Library and Information) from Andhra University, Visakhapatnam and PGDCS from University of Hyderabad. He was awarded Best Library Award First Prize in 40th Foundation Celebrations of Acharya Nagarjuna University. He has published several research papers and articles in reputed journals and conference proceedings besides contributing chapters in books. He has participated and presented research papers in several National and International Seminars and Conferences. He developed Course Materials for BLIS course under Centre for Distance Education, Acharya Nagarjuna University, Guntur. He delivered lectures as Guest Lecture/Resource Person in many Colleges/Institutions and Universities. He is the life member of Indian Library Association (ILA), Indian Association of Special Libraries and Information Centres (IASLIC), Andhra Pradesh Library Association (APLA) and also Member, PG Board of Studies in Library and Information Science, ANU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/13P2SeFA2KyoO52SK1V6e_StPwZe_FHvw?usp=sharing\" /></p>\r\n', 13461, NULL, NULL, 'Md_Zubair_Ahmad_photo.jpg', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/Md_Zubair_Ahmad_photo.jpg', NULL),
(185, 'SHAILENDRA PORIYA', 'DINESH', '1996-03-11', '08130269227', '8130269227', 'shailendraporiya2017@gmail.com', 'YOGENDRA', 'PLOT NO-178,A-BLOCK,RK WATIKA CITY, JAIPUR', 'GOVT.SCHOOL', 'JAIPUR', 'RAJESHTHAN', 303905, 'India', 'SHAILENDRA', 2147483647, 'BANK OF BARODA', 'SECTOR 31, GURGAON', 'BARB0SECTOG', 'GSYPS6205K', 'उड़ान आपके सफलता की नेटवर्क मार्केटिंग', 'SHAILENDRA PORIYA', 'Hindi', 'Others', 100, '1', '1', '<p>इस किताब में नेटवर्क मार्केटिंग से सम्बंधित ये सारे अध्याय पाये जायेगे&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. नेटवर्क मार्केटिंग/डायरेक्ट सेल्लिंग बिजनिस को क्यों करे 20 तत्व&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. समान्तर आय और गुणात्मक आय&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. महगाई की बढ़ती हुई ग्रोथ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. पैसा कमाने के चार तरीके&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. डायरेक्ट सेल्लिंग Vs ट्रडिक्शन मार्कटिंग</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. धैर्य की शक्ति</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. सकारात्मक नजरिया</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8. सीखना जरूरी है</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9&nbsp; ईमानदारी किसके प्रति होनी चाहिये</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10&nbsp; सपनो का निर्धारण&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11 सूची बनाने की कला&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12 आमंत्रण करने का तरीका&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 प्रजेंटेशन दिखा ने के तरीके&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14 फ़ॉलोअप करने के तत्व&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15 100% प्रयोग करने वाला&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>16 टीम का खिलाड़ी&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>17 टेप -किताबे - फंग्सनों&nbsp; का रोल</p>\r\n\r\n<p>18 कार्डिनल रूल&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>19 3 तरीके और 100% सफलता&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>20 वित्रिय सफलता का फार्मूला&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>21 नया सदस्य नियुक्ति करना&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>22 M L M&nbsp; में इन 10 गलतियों को कभी मत करना&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>23 नेटवर्कर कोन&nbsp; है&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>24 लीडर कोन&nbsp; है&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>25 दुनिया में चार प्रकार के लोग होते है</p>\r\n', '<p>&quot; महात्वपूर्ण बात यह नहीं है की आप कल क्या थे |<br />\r\nया आज क्या है , बल्कि महात्वपूर्ण बात तो यह है |<br />\r\nकी आप कल कहा पहुंचना चाहते है &quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>आपको अपने जीवन में चाहिए</p>\r\n\r\n<p>परिवार की आर्थिक सुरक्षा&nbsp;<br />\r\nअतिरिक्त आय&nbsp;<br />\r\nआर्थिक स्वतंत्रता&nbsp;<br />\r\nस्यम का व्यवसाय&nbsp;<br />\r\nअधिक खाली समय&nbsp;<br />\r\nव्यक्तित्व विकास&nbsp;<br />\r\nदुसरो की मदद करना&nbsp;<br />\r\nबहुत बड़ी पहचान</p>\r\n', '<p>नमस्कार दोस्तों मेरा नाम शैलेंद्र पोरिया&nbsp; है यूपी में महोबा जिले से बिलॉन्ग करता हूं&nbsp;मैं नेटवर्क मार्केटिंग को पिछले 2 सालों से कर रहा हूं 2 सालों में जो भी मैंने सीखा है वह इस किताब के अंदर शेयर करने वाला हूं जो भी लीडर इस किताब को पड़ेगा तो नेटवर्क मार्केटिंग के अंदर सफलता की उड़ान भर पाएगा</p>\r\n', 6104, NULL, NULL, 'DSC_0854-removebg-preview3.png', 'https://bfcgroup.in//assets/asf_authorMail/profilePic/DSC_0854-removebg-preview3.png', NULL);
